## Quick Checklist for New Skills
- [ ] Create `.skill` package directory
- [ ] Write SKILL.md with proper frontmatter
- [ ] Implement scripts with error handling
- [ ] Add templates/references as needed
- [ ] Test scripts independently
- [ ] Register in src/data/skills.ts
- [ ] Add markdown to skills/ directory
- [ ] Verify npm run build passes
- [ ] Create PR with demo/examples
- [ ] Assign to Copilot if delegating further work
